reviews.text: Thoroughly enjoyed both soft shell crab and prawn paper roll. Crab is not greasy, and prawn roll was a good balance of veg and prawn. Fresh ingredients and delicious!
Repeated bad customer service experiences. Though food taste good but waiters/waitress are rude. Not a good option.

I don't know why but it seems as if the owner doesn't care. Almost from the moment my group came in, everything was just bad. No sooner than we sat down, there were mosquitoes buzzing around. We moved to another table, which had poor air circulation even though the air conditioner was right overhead. One of the waiter guys said not to order anything fried as their fryer was broken. The Hainan chicken was meager, half a bird with three sauces (ginger, oyster, and vinegar) and a large bowl of rice. I noticed that the kitchen area was filthy and disorganized. As we left, the sliding glass door didn't work. Not coming back!
Very dirty place, there were flies flying around the restaurant. The waiters were extremely rude. Food came and it was cold and stale. I think I got food poisoning there.
I agree and not a good restauant. surely not come again

result.name: 大頭蝦餐廳

reviews.text: 好吃😀😀😀

本身都幾喜歡食越南菜，貪這間價錢較相宜，所以之前間中都會去食。

整體食物質素都還可以，但有時又會幾差，可是最大問題係食物衛生情況，試過幾次食完都有些攪肚！

初期去覺得員工態度好差，尤其有位高大四眼佬，成日大聲講賭馬，但後來跟老闆熟絡了，其他員工亦變得有善了，會否再光顧都要考慮吓。
食物質素好，服務員態度親切
Thoroughly enjoyed both soft shell crab and prawn paper roll. Crab is not greasy, and prawn roll was a good balance of veg and prawn. Fresh ingredients and delicious!
落錯單，又漏單。生牛河牛肉還可以，但個湯唔得。撈檬唔好食，啲檬粉硬又鞋。凍檸茶有蜜糖味。
